# Common Interview Mistakes

❌ Internet and Web are the same.

✅ The Internet is the network. The Web is a service that runs on the Internet.

---

❌ IP Address and MAC Address are the same.

✅ IP is a logical address, while MAC is a physical address.

---

❌ Router and Switch perform the same function.

✅ Router connects networks, while a Switch connects devices within the same network.

---

❌ A Port identifies a device.

✅ A Port identifies an application or service running on a device.

